Package: diggs
Title: Delineation-Informed Geographic Ground Selection
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Al", "Irvine", email = "al@newgraphenvironment.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("New Graph Environment Ltd.", role = "cph")
  )
Description: Interactive Shiny app for selecting historic orthophoto imagery
    from the BC Data Catalogue. Draw polygons or upload a custom AOI, filter
    by year/media/scale, view estimated photo footprints, and export
    selections to CSV. Built on the fly package for spatial photo operations.
